Preprocess aistpp:
    python data/preprocess_aistpp.py



Train diffusion model:
    # single GPU (debug)
    python train.py -n camdm --epoch 100 --batch_size 512 --diffusion_steps 4 -i data/pkls/aistpp_g1.pkl --past_frame 0 --future_frame 150

    # 8 GPUs (DDP)
    torchrun --nproc_per_node=8 train.py -n camdm --epoch 100 --batch_size 512 --diffusion_steps 4 -i data/pkls/aistpp_g1.pkl --past_frame 0 --future_frame 150



Visualize the training results:
    python /root/workspace/CAMDM/external/GMR/scripts/vis_gt_pred_comparison.py --input_dir /root/workspace/CAMDM/PyTorch/save/camdm_aistpp_g1/train_samples \
    --output_path /root/workspace/CAMDM/gt_pred_comparison.mp4
